    public interface Set151Interface<Q>
extends java.util.Collection<Q>
    This is an interface which models a Collection that contains no duplicate elements. It models the mathematical set abstraction. This interface is based on the Java Set interface, but there are substantial differences.

    An additional stipultation is that no constructor will construct a set containing duplicate elements. CS151, project 3.
